reviews.review_text: Friday Night In The City Never forget the everyone hitting the streets around 5 for quitting time.  Or the cops storming up that lot across the street which was always happening.  After asking some guy who appeared 2 be homeless on that top level 4 a light.  Or if he wanted puff.  Opps, John Law and he turned around and busted some shady cats. Anyway,  Decent show.  Good times w/ great friends.

Not Much Here Jerry is half in and half out this show
No Highlights
